{"tid":1346214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好灰心...","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:30:18.000Z","uid":35082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce008e71d505e56bfb7e25bcb44f448b55fde8a4","tid":1346214,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"尋晚睇live真係好嬲好無助<br />\n亦都好心痛點解香港可以變到咁得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但灰心真係解決唔到問題！！！<br />\n大家更加要努力做嘢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向:<br />\n中上環開槍當然要搞，<br />\n但大家諗下對班平民/港豬/藍絲邊樣重要啲？一定係元朗警黑合作！<br />\n因為切身影響佢地自己<br />\n更重要係兩者都係同一戰線，<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">獨立調查委員會</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n打人冇警察到同唔拉人一定要大做文章，<br />\n大肚婆/平民被打都好重要！<br />\n重有何妖！佢係保皇黨一員，即係同民賤聯好好朋友，咁大家一定要話比其他人知先得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大家都好灰，<br />\n但不如諗下點解要出黑社會呢啲低級招數？<br />\n係咪上面已經開始急？定有其他原因？<br />\n至少今次出黑社會令民意繼續係哋呢邊！<br />\n<br />\n愈黑暗我地愈唔可以放棄，共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n講得1999，有錯歡迎指正同討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73daa7b39cce3e97e317805d14ad9bd0b068c003","tid":1346214,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa43de7698cb930c7c5381f184388e058255ec9f","tid":1346214,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634609badde574e123904b79b398fb622f1c1fb5","tid":1346214,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2450327688378864?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvid